      <p class="- topic/p ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Change Caption</uicontrol> block is available only for the   <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Modify Form</uicontrol> event as the logic of this event is triggered before the form is generated and you change the caption for the appropriate field.</p>
